      • LightBinPackingPropagator

        public LightBinPackingPropagator(String[] labels,
                                 solver.variables.IntVar[][] l,
                                 int[][] s,
                                 solver.variables.IntVar[] b)
        constructor of the FastBinPacking global constraint
        Parameters:
        labels - the label describing each dimension
        l - array of nbBins variables, each figuring the total size of the items assigned to it, usually initialized to [0, capacity]
        s - array of nbItems variables, each figuring the item size. Only the LB will be considered!
        b - array of nbItems variables, each figuring the possible bins an item can be assigned to, usually initialized to [0, nbBins-1]
